REQUIREDOW
========================
Implement the following steps:

1) Incoming Call Webhook
- Endpoint: /api/call/incoming
- Receives:
  - caller_id
  - queue_id
  - agent_ext
  - call_id

2) Phone Normalization
- Normalize Egyptian phone numbers
- Remove country codes, leading zeros, formatting issues

3) Lead Lookup
- Search lead by phone
- If exists → return lead
- If NOT:
  - Create new lead:
    - status = NEW
    - source = CALL
    - phone = caller_id
    - tenant_id required

4) Screen Pop (Real-time)
- Send real-time event to agent UI:
  - Lead info (or "New Lead")
  - Phone number
  - Previous activities (if exist)

5) Auto Assignment
- Assign lead.owner_id = agent_id

6) Create Call Activity
- On call start:
  - type = call
  - status = in_progress
  - lead_id
  - agent_id
  - start_time

7) Call End Event
- Endpoint: /api/call/end
- Receives:
  - call_id
  - duration
  - hangup_cause

8) Update Activity
- status = completed
- duration
- end_time

9) Mandatory Outcome
- Agent MUST select:
  - Interested
  - Not Interested
  - Callback
  - Wrong Number

10) Next Action Enforcement
- If Callback → create scheduled activity
- If No Answer → retry task
- If Interested → move to QUALIFIED

11) Lead Status Update
- NEW → CONTACTED or QUALIFIED or LOST

12) Call Recording
- Store recording URL
- Link to activity

13) Automation Rules
- Missed call → create callback task
- No response → reminder
- VIP → notify manager

